data.title: Top films of 1934
data.meta_description: A list of 9 films compiled on Letterboxd, including L'Atalante (1934), It Happened One Night (1934), The Thin Man (1934), Twentieth Century (1934) and Man of Aran (1934). About this list: Meus filmes favoritos lançados originalmente em 1934, em ordem de preferência. Não consta: "A Sereia"(Muteki), Minoru Murata My favorite films originally released in 1934, in order of preference. Missing: "The Mermaid" (Muteki), Minoru Murata.
data.text: Letterboxd is an independent service created by a small team, and we rely mostly on the support of our members to maintain our site and apps. Please consider upgrading to a Pro account—for less than a couple bucks a month, you’ll get cool additional features like all-time and annual stats pages (example), the ability to select (and filter by) your favorite streaming services, and no ads!
